  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e4150f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3VvwbGpEMnMMfPLPgbibicelS7VBic98ZkwRO4VZ4FNwfqRFdyGRn5d1SCvFQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">上周，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">钉钉开了一场信息量巨大的发布会，掏出了AI 钉钉 1.1 新版本。坦白说，在很长一段时间里，钉钉在我心中，就是一个纯粹的办公符号。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这次发布会后，我会更加愿意在日常生活遇到的痛点也试试看用钉钉解决了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在新版钉钉里，首页变成了一个叫钉钉ONE的页面，它会默认过滤掉群聊里的废话，把关键任务重构成信息流。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0342592592592592\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020164\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2434a57f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3VvwW1qzeOJaic4jIa7CSAQnHPibmGQ1MeZConajRsZBVNEFovexVH4v4bGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次更新好用的AI功能有很多，AI搜问里还接入了Qwen Plus和Max，DeepSeek，豆包，Kimi，连GPT-4o和Gemini 2.5 Pro两个上古真神都有，一篇文章也写不完。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，我还是想从一个更真实的，甚至和工作毫无关系的场景说起。我想聊聊这次我去马来西亚亚庇三天旅行中，高频率用到的一个功能，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI听记</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">亚庇这个地方很有意思，一个不大的城市里（基本走路市中心就走完了），生活着马来人、华人、菲律宾人，还有当地的原住民。所以一天聊下来，你会同时听到英文、普通话、粤语，甚至还有一些马来语。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对多元的语言环境的挑战，十月份在西班牙我尝试用deepseek做菜单翻译，这次我跟口袋里的钉钉一起挑战。面对面实时翻译。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0212962962962964\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020167\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73a2aed2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3VvwYr2WZN3lVp1TQhuJrk0ZUsh9q96AzhdkFWuuyYyBsqTgdAuTB0rREA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(143, 149, 158) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">左边导游讲解实时转录，右边是跟导游聊天</span></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为有了实时翻译的第一感觉这次花钱请的本地导游值了，这个翻译是可以实时合成音频的。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我用的是当地Orange的电话卡，实测下来，中英互译加上语音合成，几乎感觉不到延迟。无论是跟小贩砍价买榴莲（强推黑刺和猫山王），还是在餐厅里磕磕巴巴地点菜，甚至是在爬山去看大王花的路上和向导闲聊，我都可以开着这个实时翻译。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这彻底改变了我的旅行体验。之前去泰国旅游，因为语言不通，我和当地导游几乎是零交流，他负责带路，我负责看景拍照片。但这次，因为有了AI当免费的翻译官，我能了解到，亚庇原来是马来西亚消费第二高的城市，我们之所以在7-11和Orange便利店里找不到什么本地零食，是因为这里的物品基本都从吉隆坡进口，而亚庇又是离吉隆坡最远的城市。我还知道，这里的手机市场，几乎被华为、vivo和OPPO瓜分了，连苹果都很少见。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7518518518518519\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020166\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5be2cfd7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3Vvwx6eEUdgXIj9Fzs9sMAWRrSibppNWWmiaAsxF0jREq3IQH7d0QIgsnHIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些琐碎但生动的信息，是以往任何旅行攻略里都不会告诉我的。它们像一块块拼图，让我对这个陌生的地方，有了一种更融入当地的理解。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">旅途中还有一个痛点，长时间坐车晕车，或者周围环境超级吵比方说在船上的时候，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我又不想错过导游的介绍。这时候，AI听记的图文纪要就会直接生成类似信息图的摘要，我可以不二次重听音频，直接看图文就能get到重点。甚至在录音的同时，我还可以随时拍下眼前的画面，比方说我这里就是一个好看的路牌，这些图片会作为笔记的一部分被保存下来。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.687962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=924b81f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3Vvw9GefcEFrp1icOFQwl7bfqZrjDvqFKACKEL0ibdev6tq0kbbNIO3ibqD9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两天在旅游担心错过发布会啥的，所以我中途还挂着AI听记来看大牛们推荐的2025AI工具合集，这时候AI听记的声纹识别就有更好的用法了。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 5px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6212962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020165\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d212d7f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmr4OTUEqr8sjMiaRD7e3VvweiawWHowL5BFcMlPE8KEJeD8IFsVHkYGkK9vRZIJ15mIX9icn6lnS3EA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">通常情况下，如果我一边播放视频，一边录音，那么AI会认为视频里所有人说的话，都是我说的。但在开启声纹识别后，它能清晰地区分出我的声音和来自播放设备的声音。这样，我就可以一边听会，一边随时插入我自己的评论和思考。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"marg